{"tid":1886693,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"西環集中營：林鄭抗疫犯眾憎 搶功卸膊有前科 - 季陶","createTime":"2020-02-19T05:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T07:53:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0db7aad1ca0d529007b0a15ef9e9aee34eab09","tid":1886693,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200219/D62RLLAXRZ7QYD2VARX75IJENA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200219%2FD62RLLAXRZ7QYD2VARX75IJENA%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=faa063b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200219%2FD62RLLAXRZ7QYD2VARX75IJENA%2F&h=e499c3d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200219/D62RLLAXRZ7QYD2VARX75IJENA/</a><br />\n<br />\n西環集中營：林鄭抗疫犯眾憎 搶功卸膊有前科 - 季陶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200219/large/1582044623_fd27.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200219%2Flarge%2F1582044623_fd27.gif&h=68ac5edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港針對武漢肺炎防疫工作，一直被批評做得較澳門差，更將矛頭直指特首林鄭月娥領導失誤，但她昨日被問到有關問題，竟然叫記者不要拿澳門與香港比較，將原本要問責問題，變成與她完全無關。有熟悉林鄭的政界中人指，這是林鄭慣技，「小小功就誇大好多倍，一發現出事，唔係卸就係扮唔關佢事」，而林鄭這種作風，當面對危機時候，不單令不滿她的人更憤怒，甚至連支持者也對她失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n該政界人士與林鄭算是識於微時，隨林鄭高升，兩人也不時有交手，他對季陶笑言，林鄭一向領功、爭表現從來「不甘後人」，「佢睇到有功、可以有掌聲，一定第一時間出嚟領功，仲會將佢做咗幾多嘢誇大好多倍，等上級、市民覺得佢好勁」，但當事件對她不利、又或碰了釘，「佢就扮到成件事唔關佢事」。<br />\n<br />\n他以當年林鄭做發展局局長，誓言全面取締新界丁屋僭建為例，當年林鄭以為可立功爭取民望，「起晒鑼鼓話嚴厲執法取締僭建村屋，仲講到正式宣戰」，但當她知道不能得罪原居民，即「縮埋」不再講，他記得林鄭升任政務司司長後，曾在電台節目中為嚴打僭建被追數，「佢好嘢呀，話發展局屬財政司司長之下，佢對丁屋僭建跟進工作唔係完全好掌握，就咁卸咗隻鑊畀曾俊華」。<br />\n<br />\n面對抗疫之戰，該政界人士指林鄭只是故技重施，「搞唔掂、俾人鬧就唔講、唔提、話冇得比較，卸咗隻鑊算，而唔係去面對問題」，但林鄭不知這種態度令建制也越來越多人對她失去信心，「好多建制派已覺林鄭係佢哋大包袱，想盡快甩咗佢」。<br />\n<br />\n季陶<br />\n周一、三、五刊出"},{"pid":"dee88f47bf3495473cce45f43c6790d98c271c70","tid":1886693,"uid":4761,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"政界中人係唔係就係曾俊華"},{"pid":"1dab769c7ca2163651eff9bf9fd6b67f304673f1","tid":1886693,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a149d92ea7d6f1117fd13b20776bc33851f1dcde","tid":1886693,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"澳門 0 : 2 香港"},{"pid":"fbf84a8687cfb5a84253f965c68204114c092309","tid":1886693,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"個高官係楊立門？"},{"pid":"bb09749056a7fb5f5699cb538ad8e516409df756","tid":1886693,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賣港狗共呢幾日明顯夾埋5大免費電媒，係咁loop用毒船黎spin走武漢啦！今日冚家超仲的起個狗官樣屌架佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔配合？？咁支狗呢？？！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共同支共不嬲至叻抽死人尾水白事當功積，口交部仲吓吓一涉及外國睇有位賺就話係外交事務擦存在感添！！<br />\n<br />\n但大家有<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇留意，上鋪賓佬單野都仲有外交部搶Fo，點撚解今次冇嘅？？</span></span></span></span></strong></blockquote>師兄你屌柒梁志健真係好撚正，請受我一拜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">至屌鬼係臨支支TVB拍雜種廢炎至自爆個昆C9廢老故仔，隨時完全又係狗政PR屎片劇本囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！</span></strong></span></span></span><br />\nl"},{"pid":"da280f2d734c528e1ec6b2c4361c49c935cb604b","tid":1886693,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"打工仔心態做領導者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b0f39c80ce6cc8106819bac5957d90b5dec6ca","tid":1886693,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da280f2d734c528e1ec6b2c4361c49c935cb604b","tid":1886693,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"打工仔心態做領導者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"AO政府工心態<br />\n擅於執行，但政策同大方向無自己嘅理念同理論支撐"},{"pid":"f85215ca26abe599aca8b0198910f55dc66d8929","tid":1886693,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"「好多建制派已覺林鄭係佢哋大包袱，想盡快甩咗佢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上面支持林太，建制都夠膽割席，係唔係扭計要射多幾十億維穩費落黎。經過區議會選舉一役，應該知道全香港選民都會將正苦同建制綑綁式投票，如果唔係都唔會咁橙啦。係可見嘅9月立法會選舉，係封關立場建制派經常顧左右而言他，望就望唔好死人社區爆發，如果唔係，媒體炒作下，死返幾百人，立法會選舉會更加難睇。"},{"pid":"82ee85f8f8939b0bcf59afda37d8f129f731ebaf","tid":1886693,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da280f2d734c528e1ec6b2c4361c49c935cb604b","tid":1886693,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"打工仔心態做領導者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"做得林太個位，歷任最有自由意志嘅應該都係得曾特首，如果唔係咁有Guts佢應該都唔使坐。陰謀論D去睇應該就係唔肯執行23條國民教育等政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a4bfa6e0e6233b8c127ec2184ce51e57cf3ae8","tid":1886693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7b0f39c80ce6cc810681